author: rumblxphish
title: rumblxphish
text:
I ordered an LS2 Arrow Matrix helmet from FC-Moto.de and for a seller in Germany, the delivery time to Houston, TX USA was not bad at all. They gave me the tracking number for the shipment, which I was able to track and follow during the entire delivery process.
I highly recommend this seller. They are top-notch and provide excellent communication and customer service.
Thanks you FC-Moto.de for an excellent product and a wonderful overseas buying experience.
